items.text:
Casting Call for Short 10-15 minutes called Repossession 

This is a  darkly comic short about ambition, fame, and the unexpected horrors lurking behind a routine job.

Casting call for the characters 
Kyle
 A seasoned presenter clinging to relevance in a changing media landscape. Desperate for a comeback, he takes one last job‚Äîblinded by ambition, even when the warning signs turn supernatural.
 Playing Age: Early 30s to mid 40s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Male
Spencer
 Kyle‚Äôs loyal second-in-command, tasked with shaping the show‚Äôs content. Often dragged into eerie locations, Spencer must confront whether he‚Äôs valued as a partner‚Äîor just a pawn.
 Playing Age: Mid 20s to Mid 30s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Male
Carla Curses
 A flashy social media psychic with a massive following and a hunger for viral fame. Her pursuit of a haunted object leads to possession‚Äîtransforming her into something savage and inhuman.
 Playing Age: 20s to 30s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Female
Frank
Carla‚Äôs trusted cameraman, now shattered by the night‚Äôs horrors. Haunted and fragile, his trauma slowly pulls him into the house‚Äôs darkness.
Playing Age: 30s to 40s
Ethnicity: Any
Physicality: Tall and lanky
Gender: Male

Filming will take place in the Liverpool/Merseyside area, United Kingdom. Looking to film middle to end of January 2026 
Please apply only if you're based locally.
For more details, contact: houndsoftheroundtable@gmail.com

Please note we do not reply to comments or direct Facebook messages. Thank you!

items.text:
**UL√òNNET**

Vi er et hold fra Potemkin, Den Jyske Filmskole, der er i gang med vores afgangsprojekt

Vi s√∏ger en mand i spillealderen 18-23 til hovedrollen Milo

Kort om historien:
En ung mand med et spiralerende heroinmisbrug vender hjem til sin syge mor for f√∏rste gang i m√•nedsvis. Han kommer for at bede om penge - men ender som et stille opg√∏r mellem k√¶rlighed og skam. Vi √∏nsker ikke at lave en film som glorificerer stoffer, men om, hvordan det nedbryder de st√¶rkeste relationer mellem mennesker.

Om rollen:
Milo er 23 og fanget i sit eget forfald. Bag afh√¶ngigheden gemmer sig en s√∏n, der stadig elsker sin mor, men ikke l√¶ngere kan b√¶re at blive set af hende. Skylden, k√¶rligheden og skammen eksisterer side om side i ham.
Rollen kr√¶ver en skuespiller med evnen til at udtrykke mere gennem stilhed end gennem ord - en fysisk og f√∏lelsesm√¶ssig tilstedev√¶relse, hvor sm√• reaktioner og blikke fort√¶ller alt.

Praktisk:
Optagelserne finder sted i Aarhus den 24. og 25. november.
Der vil v√¶re fuld forplejning p√• settet, men vi vil ikke kunne betale k√∏n, transport eller overnatning.

Hvis du er interesseret i at blive taget i betragtning til rollen, bedes du indsende et kort selftape af dummy teksten, der er vedh√¶ftet i opslaget. Send det meget gerne til mailen nedenfor.

items.summary:
**UL√òNNET**

Vi er et hold fra Potemkin, Den Jyske Filmskole, der er i gang med vores afgangsprojekt

Vi s√∏ger en mand i spillealderen 18-23 til hovedrollen Milo

Kort om historien:
En ung mand med et spiralerende heroinmisbrug vender hjem til sin syge mor for f√∏rste gang i m√•nedsvis. Han kommer for at bede om penge - men ender som et stille opg√∏r mellem k√¶rlighed og skam. Vi √∏nsker ikke at lave en film som glorificerer stoffer, men om, hvordan det nedbryder de st√¶rkeste relationer mellem mennesker.

Om rollen:
Milo er 23 og fanget i sit eget forfald. Bag afh√¶ngigheden gemmer sig en s√∏n, der stadig elsker sin mor, men ikke l√¶ngere kan b√¶re at blive set af hende. Skylden, k√¶rligheden og skammen eksisterer side om side i ham.
Rollen kr√¶ver en skuespiller med evnen til at udtrykke mere gennem stilhed end gennem ord - en fysisk og f√∏lelsesm√¶ssig tilstedev√¶relse, hvor sm√• reaktioner og blikke fort√¶ller alt.

Praktisk:
Optagelserne finder sted i Aarhus den 24. og 25. november.
Der vil v√¶re fuld forplejning p√• settet, men vi vil ikke kunne betale k√∏n, transport eller overnatning.

Hvis du er interesseret i at blive taget i betragtning til rollen, bedes du indsende et kort selftape af dummy teksten, der er vedh√¶ftet i opslaget. Send det meget gerne til mailen nedenfor.

Vi h√•ber, at projektet v√¶kker din nysgerrighed - og at du har lyst til at tage del i fort√¶llingen om Milo og hans mor.

items.text:
Hi! 

I‚Äôm currently casting a well paid shoot for an alcohol brand

As it‚Äôs advertising for alcohol all cast legally need to be at least 25 (production will ask for id to prove this if shortlisted by client) however the concept for the project is quite youthful so max age should be 30. 

Casting Brief: 

Looking for European girls with coloured hair (think red, blue, pink, green, berry, purple) or happy to have their hair coloured for the shoot. 

Looking for European boys with facial hair (a moustache and/or beard - bonus if you have an interesting hair cut too) 

This is a London shoot so looking for London based people only. 

**Shoot Dates: **Thursday 27th + Friday 28th November

Talent to attend both shoot days in London on Location

Based on a 10 hour shoot day including an additional hour for lunch

**Fitting Date:** Monday 24th November, 1-2 hours in London (between 9am and 6pm)

**Talent Age: **All Talent to be over 25 and passport or ID needs to be provided at the time of shortlist to confirm this 

**Talent Rates:**

Talent Day Rates - ¬£600 per person per day

Talent Usage* ¬£5,000 per model

*Usage not guaranteed however all talent are shot in groups so this is very likely to be confirmed

**Talent Wardrobe:**

Talent will be required to bring a couple of outfits to the shoot which will be briefed by the wardrobe stylist

and either brought to the fitting or photographed before the shoot.

¬£50 per person (total not per day)

To submit please fill in this form : 

[https://airtable.com/apprDbNv50EdHz0RT/pagpszb0AEzQg5XCi/form](https://airtable.com/apprDbNv50EdHz0RT/pagpszb0AEzQg5XCi/form)

And, please upload your self tape here: [https://www.dropbox.com/request/s2OXkOWhOSaif9oUoaCR](https://www.dropbox.com/request/s2OXkOWhOSaif9oUoaCR)

The deadline is 10AM, Monday 17th November. 

No requests, no PM‚Äôs 

Thank you! 

www.unit-c.co

Are you a passionate supporter of Barcelona FC? Are you based in London or planning to be in the city on November 25th for the Chelsea v Barcelona match? We want to hear from you!

We're looking for enthusiastic fans to take part in a short, 20-minute interview with our presenter outside Stamford Bridge before the match. You'll have the chance to share your thoughts on the team and players, and we'll pay you ¬£150 for your time.

To apply, simply record a video answering the following questions and send it to email in the ad.

- What's your name, age, and location?

- Do you think Ferran Torres is underrated? Why?

- If Fermin L√≥pez played in the English league, would he be getting more hype? How much would he be worth?

*Interview Details:*

- Date: 25th November

- Location: Outside Stamford Bridge, London

- Time: TBC

- Duration: 20 minutes

- Compensation: ¬£150

Don't miss this opportunity to share your passion for Barcelona FC with our LADbible audience! Apply now and let's get talking!

**CASTING CALL ‚Äì BRUCE (NORTH LONDON, END OF NOVEMBER):**

Seeking an **actor 18+ who can play **14-16 for the role of **Bruce** in the short film *The Unseen*. Bruce is a quiet, internal, emotionally intense boy living with his two sisters under an abusive father with a strong attachment to his mum who‚Äôs currently in rehab. The story builds toward a dramatic family confrontation and a powerful emotional climax 

**We‚Äôre looking for someone who can:**
* Convey emotion through subtle expression and presence
* Play vulnerable, internalised moments
* Handle tense and dramatic scenes

**Details:**
* **Unpaid (expenses covered)**
* **Shoots end of November**
* **Location:** North London 

To apply please send an email to:
* Jasonvalletta04@icloud.com

Reposting because lead actor dropped out!

DRAMA SHORT FILM CASTING CALL ‚Äì In His Care

SYNOPSIS: When granddaughter, Red, stops receiving letters from her sick grandmother she insists on visiting. Surprised, she finds a man who claims to be her grandmother‚Äôs new carer. As he continues to ask strange questions and refuses to let Red see her, she realises the man is taking advantage of her poor grandmother, using medicines to make her sicker. When confronted the man becomes enraged and is forced to kill little Red. 

Wanted: 1 actors (F) for exciting new short film ‚ÄòIn His Care‚Äô. Shooting in Hertfordshire, w/c 24th November, student project from an award-winning Film & TV course.

- RED (Female, 24 ‚Äì 30)

- Description: Mid to late 20s

Red is a simple, reserved girl. She is kind and holds herself highly. But when it comes to her grandma, she is extremely protective, fierce even. She is perceptive and head strong and will do anything to find what‚Äôs happening at grandma‚Äôs house.

- Height: 5‚Äô5 ‚Äì 5‚Äô9

- Appearance: Red is a modest girl. She dresses simple when visiting her grandmother, always wearing the infamous red scarf that her grandmother gave her.

- Travel Expenses / Food Paid

please contact sheldonkieran4@gmail.com

Once Upon a Wish Events are on the search for a Father Christmas for our ‚ÄúThe Toy Workshop ‚Äú event on the following dates 

23rd and 24th december at 
Millbrook garden Gravesend an INDOOR EVENT no thermals required!! 

23rd dec- Appear for 20 minutes in the following time slots- 930am-1030am , 11am-12 midday , 1-2pm and 230-330pm 

24th dec- Appear for 20 minutes in the following time slots- 1030-1130 am  , 12 midday-1pm and  , 2 -3 pm  

Free parking, x2 free hot drinks provided and a hot meal . 

All items provided ie- costume, beard , wig, moustache boots and eyebrows 

Inbox if available and to discuss fee

## **CASTING CALL ‚Äì ‚ÄúTale of Two‚Äù (Short Film)**

**Logline:**
*‚ÄúTale of Two‚Äù* is a portrait short film about women‚Äôs strength, focusing on our shared experiences rather than our differences. Through small, intimate scenes, we witness key moments in the lives of two women as they navigate hardship, love, and resilience in parallel journeys.

**Production Details:**
* **Location:** Downtown Vancouver
* **Shoot Dates:** 1-3 days ‚Äì end of January
* **Format:** MOS (no sync sound) ‚Äì performances will rely heavily on expressive, facial acting
* **Union Status:** Non-Union / Volunteer Passion Project
* **Compensation:** Volunteer basis with **great meals, greater company, and IMDb credit**.
Select roles (requiring multiple full days) will receive a **small honorarium**.

**To Submit:**
Please send your **headshot and CV/demo reel**, which **role** you‚Äôre applying for and a **self-tape** with the attached actions **taleoftwofilm@gmail.com**.
Include a **slate** with your **name, age, height,** and any **unavailable dates**.
**Submission Deadline:** *November 25th at midnight.*

Casting Call!

*Starchild* is a sci-fi drama that follows the story of two scientists, Vanessa and Tanner as they take separate paths to deal with their grief. Vanessa through faith, and Tanner through science. It's not until they discover the origins of life itself, that they reconcile to start a family of their own. 

The film is heartfelt, honest, and powerful.

Please send resume, headshot, and (if applicable) demo reel to starchildcasting@gmail.com

Hertfordshire Zoo is looking for jolly, enthusiastic, and festive individuals to bring the magic of Christmas to life this year at **Hertfordshire Zoo in Broxbourne, Hertfordshire.**

**What We‚Äôre Looking For:**
* A warm, friendly personality with plenty of festive spirit
* Confidence interacting with children and families
* Reliability and professionalism
* Previous performance or grotto experience (preferred but not essential)
* We have a mixture of performance elf and grotto elf work available

**When You‚Äôll Work:**

The dates we are currently still looking for people are:
* 26th November (4:30pm-8:30pm)
* 29th November (9:30am-4:00pm)
* 30th November (9:00am-5:00pm)

Hi everyone! I‚Äôd love to invite you all to see our **award-nominated, five-star dark comedy** currently touring the UK that‚Äôs coming to London **next week** for a fortnight at the Drayton Arms in Kensington!

‚ÄòYes, he's in a celebrations tub. No, he's not in with the bounties.‚Äô

Aaron, an unemployed entertainer, has stolen his dad's ashes and hidden them in a tub of chocolates. As he journeys toward St. Ives to scatter them, we discover the reasons behind his theft, and witness a suspenseful chase with the police hot on his heels. 

Written and performed by Oscar Brudenall-Jones and directed by Esalan Gates (5-star, BroadwayWorld UK Nominee ‚Äì Best New Production), this dark comedy explores grief in a post-pandemic world, as well as sperm bank strikes and why you shouldn't lose your rag at an old person.

Produced by To The Tooth Theatre, this is comedy with a bite.

It‚Äôs a wrap! Six Commercials with 50 Actors from MA to TX to RI and back to RI for 3 more this week!!  4 Picture cars in TX - RI!! Locations in RI!  

On Set Wrangler, Child Welfare Worker and Production Assistant!  

Catering and Crafty for 4 days! 

I have a new business: ACTORDASH - I don‚Äôt just cast ‚Äòem! I deliver them to set!

I jumped in feet first starting in August 2025, and although we still have some administrative work to do; we are officially wrapped!

I am now on Holiday Break and will be gearing up for more filming in January 2026!

During this break I will be doing a massive Talent Scout starting in Rhode Island!

I know I can easily find everyone I need for our Massachusetts needs with a simple post! But, I‚Äôve found it harder to find Actors in Rhode Island.

I am also planning a Karaoke Holiday Party for the first time since before Covid!  If you‚Äôd like to attend send an email to:

JodiPurdyCasting@gmail.com
Subj:  Holiday Party 2025

On another good note - my client is looking into signing a SAG Contract in 2026!  

But for the time being I will be casting Non-Union Actors and Real People to portray Doctors, Nurses, Medical Personnel and Patients from all walks of life living in Rhode Island.

Submit to:

JodiPurdyCasting@gmail.com
Subj: RI Resident NU Actor Real Person

Share:

Jodi Purdy (Name)
111-111-1111 (cell)
jodipurdycasting@gmail.com (email)
Weymouth, MA (location)

DO NOT TYPE (name, cell, email, location) ONLY YOUR INFO which I cut and paste!

Share:

Photos, videos, reels, links, resume, etc.

Celebrating tonight at the Orpheum Theater in Boston at a Dark Star Orchestra show with 3 of my besties!!

üåç **You're Invited: Alex Fil's 27th Birthday Bash in Covent Garden ‚Äì I'm Alone in the UK & Need Your Company! üéÇ‚ú®**

Hey London (and world wanderers)! I'm Alex Fil ‚Äì Ukrainian TV presenter living my London adventure **but completely alone here, with no one to celebrate my birthday with**. Turning 27 on **28 November at 7:30 PM** ‚Äì join me for an open, fun-filled evening at **Apple Market, Covent Garden (WC2E 8RF)**!

I'll bring some cake & drinks to share, but since **I have no friends or family nearby** (and don't know who's coming!), bring your faves: snacks, bubbly, balloons, or just your amazing self. Let's turn my lonely day into a pop-up party under the market lights ‚Äì good vibes, stories, and maybe a spontaneous sing-along? üòä

**RSVP: Comment below or DM me!** Tag friends who can make a stranger's day. #CoventGardenParty #LondonBirthdayBash #AloneInUK #BringYourVibes

CASTING CALL FOR NEW PLAY!
--------------------------------

A New Comedic play by Zack Faulks, *Bulimia is My Roman Empire* follows a group of Servants as they attempt to assassinate the Emperor. They discover that power may not be all that they had once desired. Learning that their target is engaged in a number of self-destructive behaviours, our conspirators are forced to follow down a long rabbit hole of strange diets, machismo, and fascism should they want to prove that they deserve the right to rule. As a satire of manhood, ultimately no one‚Äôs happy with where they end up.

For more information check out the images below!

Deadline to submit is Nov. 29, 2025 at 12:00pm.

--------------------
Find us at www.greattrashproductions.ca

items.text:
Casting Call (Non-Union) for COUPLES - Paid

Looking for actors to play the role of clients in a simulated therapy session. The video clips will be used in an online training system for counselors and psychologists. The sessions include some scripted elements to prepare, and then some improv with prompts.

We are currently interested in filming with mature couples, queer couples, interracial couples, or throuples/polycules of various gender identity combinations. All ages, all gender expressions/identities, all ethnicities, and persons with disabilities are welcome. 

All experience levels with acting are welcome, including experienced actors with less experienced partners. We are committed to making this a respectful and safe process, with open communication and respect for boundaries.

Comfortable English fluency is required.

Immediate filming dates are November 14 to 18, based on actor availability, but more will occur in the future so please submit if you're interested at all.

Location is downtown Vancouver - Gastown. Pay is $90 CAD per performer, with the expectation of some prepared material, studio session duration: 1 hour

Please email phil@skillsetter.com with your headshot and resume, as well as some information about you and your partner, such as gender identities, age, cultural/racial backgrounds. If you've submitted for a past session, you're welcome to submit again. We do sometimes receive more submissions than we are able to respond to, but we do read them all, and we do save your submissions for future consideration.

items.text:
Die Vorbereitungen laufen weiter auf Hochtouren. Unser Projekt steht inzwischen auf einem stabilen Fundament, und die Crew w√§chst von Tag zu Tag. Jetzt beginnt die Phase, in der wir die passenden Schauspieler an Bord holen ‚Äì aber klar ist auch: Ein Film dieser Gr√∂√üe braucht weit mehr als nur ein starkes Ensemble.

F√ºr Viper ‚Äì Code Red haben wir die wichtigsten Bereiche definiert, die wir noch besetzen oder verst√§rken:

Aufnahmeleitung, Art Department, Beleuchtung, Budget/Finanzierung, Setbau, Casting, Catering, Camera Crew, Drehbuchunterst√ºtzung, Drehplanung, Drohnencrew, technisches Equipment, Schnitt/Editing, Fahrerteam und Transport, Ton/Sounddepartment, Grafik/Marketing, Herstellungsleitung, Hair & Make-Up, Intimit√§tskoordination (falls notwendig), Kameraabteilung, Kost√ºm, Komparsenmanagement, Locations/Motivbetreuung, Musik/Score, Produktionsb√ºro/Organisation, Produzenten/Produktionsleitung, Postproduktion inklusive VFX und Color Grading, Qualit√§tssicherung/Script Supervising, Regieassistenz, Requisiten, Waffenmeister, SFX, Stunts und Sicherheitsfachkr√§fte, Tonstudio/Mischung, Unit Management/Logistik, Distribution/Verleih, Werbung/Trailerproduktion sowie Zielgruppen-Analyse.

Ein wichtiger Punkt, auf den wir besonders stolz sind:

Viper ‚Äì Code Red ist offiziell bei IMDb gelistet.

Hier der Eintrag:

https://www.imdb.com/title/tt38784411/

Und jetzt der Teil, der f√ºr viele spannend ist:

Wir √∂ffnen erneut die Bewerbungsphase f√ºr Schauspieler, Nebenrollen und Kleinstrollen.

Wir suchen Menschen mit Pr√§senz, Energie und Charakter ‚Äì egal ob mit Erfahrung oder Neueinsteiger, solange die Haltung passt. Bewerbungen sind ausdr√ºcklich wieder m√∂glich.

Dazu kommt:

Wir suchen ebenso weitere Fachkr√§fte im Bereich Requisiten, Waffen, Spezialeffekte und technische Ausstattung.

Egal ob Props-Designer, Waffenmeister, SFX-Erfahrene oder Fachleute f√ºr realistische Einsatz- und Polizeiausr√ºstung ‚Äì hier gibt es viel Raum f√ºr Profis, die Lust auf ein ernstes Projekt haben.

Gerade deshalb ist diese Phase entscheidend:

Wir positionieren uns nicht als Fanprojekt, sondern als ernstes Filmvorhaben mit klarer Struktur, professionellen Bereichen und verl√§sslichen Prozessen. Jeder, der jetzt zu uns kommt, steigt in ein Projekt ein, das nach Standards arbeitet ‚Äì nicht nach Zufall.

Parallel beginnt die Besetzung unseres Schauspiel-Ensembles: Hauptrollen, Nebenrollen, wiederkehrende Figuren sowie das komplette Phoenix-Universum rund um Phoenix One, Phoenix Two und das Phoenix HQ. Jede Rolle erh√§lt Profil, Pr√§senz und Pers√∂nlichkeit ‚Äì und wir suchen Darsteller, die genau das mitbringen: Charakter, Haltung, Ausdauer und Lust auf eine realistische, bodenst√§ndige, kraftvolle Actionwelt.

Der Cast-Aufbau l√§uft.

Die Crew w√§chst.

Die Struktur steht.

Jetzt holen wir die Menschen dazu, die Viper ‚Äì Code Red lebendig machen.

Weitere Casting-Infos folgen.

DRAMA SHORT FILM CASTING CALL ‚Äì In His Care

SYNOPSIS: When granddaughter, Red, stops receiving letters from her sick grandmother she insists on visiting. Surprised, she finds a man who claims to be her grandmother‚Äôs new carer. As he continues to ask strange questions and refuses to let Red see her, she realises the man is taking advantage of her poor grandmother, using medicines to make her sicker. When confronted the man becomes enraged and is forced to kill little Red. 

Wanted: 1 actors (F) for exciting new short film ‚ÄòIn His Care‚Äô. Shooting in Hertfordshire, w/c 24th November, student project from an award-winning Film & TV course.

- RED (Female, 24 ‚Äì 30)

- Description: Mid to late 20s

Red is a simple, reserved girl. She is kind and holds herself highly. But when it comes to her grandma, she is extremely protective, fierce even. She is perceptive and head strong and will do anything to find what‚Äôs happening at grandma‚Äôs house.

- Height: 5‚Äô5 ‚Äì 5‚Äô9

- Appearance: Red is a modest girl. She dresses simple when visiting her grandmother, always wearing the infamous red scarf that her grandmother gave her.

- Travel Expenses / Food Paid

please contact sheldonkieran4@gmail.com

items.text:
Happy Tuesday all!

I provide an affordable PAY WHAT YOU CAN showreel service for new or established actors/directors/cinematographers/comedians/hobbyists etc 

Please see samples of recent clients in the link below üòé

I'm an actor myself so I know how frustrating it can be, especially when you're starting out, to collate your footage together to get more work, without wanting to spend a fortune. 

Basically, send me your footage (or I can try and source it for you online if it's commercially aired) and I shall edit it together into a lovely reel.

For any further info / enquiries / to book my services, drop me an email and I'll respond as quick as I can:

reelsforanyone@gmail.com

I'll look forward to hearing from you.

Thanks! 

üòé

sharedPost.text:
I am Thomas Goersch from Stuttgart Germany. 
Actor and Filmdirector. 
I am making Independent Movies and some kind of Art House Underground Movies. I present my movies on International Film festivals and was lucky to receive some awards. 
But the work is not about awards and money, its about making movies for the people to think about.
My next movie is a modern love story:
An elderly man is meeting another younger, very attractive man in the Internet.  But they are from different Continents. They start a long distance relastionship ship. which is full of passion and desire. 
One day the younger man starts to ask for money, cause he is a Student and no more able to pay his bills. 
The older man is full of distrust.
Is he only there  to pay his lovers bills or is there love between them ?
A story with two endings.
One with true love and one with betrayl.

I am looking for the young attraktive Lover.
Men  25 to 42 years old,  good looking  who is able to film his parts on his own by smartshone
I am always open and honest. You can earn no money on this. but maybe there is a good film in the end promoting for you.
I guess its not necessary that an educated actor is playing this part. so feel free to get in touch

Thats me 
www.imdb.com/name/nm1591928

Get in touch under Thomas.Goersch@vodafonemail.de 

please ask for details.

*Michael Chekhov Europe* invites you to its first workshop in the new year: 

**THE MOVING SPACE: Atmosphere and Playfulness on Stage **

with **David Zinder**, Tel Aviv, **Vladimir Baicher**, Moscow, **Suzana Nikoliƒá**, Zagreb, **Ulrich Meyer-Horsch**, Hamburg

**January 29 to February 1, 2026 **in Hamburg, Germany 

The space on stage is full of life, full of energy and breath. All an actor has to do is connect to this living space. 

What happens when we dive into the world of a given play and allow ourselves to be surprised by its specific dynamics, energy, language and space? 

Michael Chekhov‚Äôs concepts of ‚ÄúAtmosphere‚Äù (‚Äúthe soul of every performance‚Äù) and ‚ÄúThe Feeling of Ease, Form, Beauty and the Whole‚Äù will guide us through this exploration. 

*Movement in Space ‚Äì Objective Atmosphere ‚Äì Spatial Relationship ‚Äì Personal Atmosphere ‚Äì Feeling of Ease, Form, Beauty and the Whole ‚Äì Organic breathing ‚Äì Playfulness ‚Äì Ensemble *

Michael Chekhov Europe Training ‚Äì module 2

Tuition fee: 450‚Ç¨ / 490‚Ç¨

More information: [[https://sfsh.de/michael-chekhov-module-2/sfsh10037/](https://sfsh.de/michael-chekhov-module-2/sfsh10037/?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQQMjIyMDM5MTc4ODIwMDg5MghjYWxsc2l0ZQEyAAEeY52GI3lQe3pjPHhDXowpGuLqIQrzJcqGyZcZh3SR3jGKGPx3ohVQgDBpaaY_aem_LqlofjR6f5SXrNzWnHvQPg&brid=aB9vxtDqrKES53cnQp0y_A)](https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsfsh.de%2Fmichael-chekhov-module-2%2Fsfsh10037%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQQMjIyMDM5MTc4ODIwMDg5MghjYWxsc2l0ZQEyAAEex7NVSBwXFESZYv0PnNVOZZnSrzpDqZTYYyPIFJFP5nZT3Q26Ztt6WS-2fEA_aem_avdglXTU1DOTHvEm2ODLWw%26brid%3DkHUv4f1OfBXrKWr9lBtxHA&h=AT3aprJLj6mz3iCe_wMtmzrhtZGIayz1KSnpU58Ex7Z3EzPlrdAAC1KuqKpynOGfS5EK5Ig9QN83EuaeroAfCpArCXGbw_dimFyj16sIOeaPH6rPkuzKw_HUwj0Asyp3ugyfD65FobRJTmjdHtFUjy3Q2Q&__tn__=-UK-R&c[0]=AT0HA0NarzIKKHpcfuGCk_r7lozXPeUvPcNPcopwlZ-UI1byChoQ3du3h8W5ximHzMBhAEXGkb_bl8TQatSz2VHJa7jDl-KVLtmeALpkJ1DA_bE9mEexuYkjuWUew5yTen0VdKvkkNsZpaSC4X3beQM387ABsSrCYXTYojujQlQB)

Contact: chekhov@sfsh.de 

This in-person workshop can be acknowledged as part of the upcoming MICHA/MCE Teachers Training.

**ISO: 15-FT Production Truck Driver (PA)  - Indie Film**

We are seeking a reliable Driver(PA) for our micro-budget indie film.

**Non-Union**

**Location:** Los Angeles Area
**Position:** 15ft Production Truck Driver
**Rate:** $18.19/hour

**Responsibilities:**
* Pick up production truck and deliver to set location
* Return to set after wrap to pick up truck and transport to next location
* Ensure safe and timely transport of production vehicle
* Loading & unloading truck with other assistance

**Work Dates:**
* Thursday, December 4, 2025 (pick up day)
* Friday, December 5, 2025
* Saturday, December 6, 2025
* Sunday, December 7, 2025
* Monday, December 8, 2025
* Tuesday, December 9, 2025
* Friday, December 12, 2025 (potentially - not definite)
* Saturday, December 13, 2025
* Sunday, December 14, 2025
* Monday, December 15, 2025
* Tuesday, December 16, 2025
* Wednesday, December 17, 2025
* Thursday, December 18, 2025 (return day)

**Hours:** These will not be full shooting days. Hours may range from 4 to 6 hours per day as needed for vehicle transport.

**Requirements:**
* Valid driver's license
* Clean driving record
* Experience driving larger vehicles/trucks preferred
* Punctual and dependable

If interested, please submit your resume, a message regarding your interest/experience, and 3 references to info@saltpicturesco.com with your availability and any questions about the position.

üé≠ **CASTING CALL ‚Äî VLYT ART SCENE STUDY**

Project: *De Nieuwe Ridderorde* ‚Äî *Temperance Knights*

Format: Recorded Scene Study + Showcase Screening

Language: English & Afrikaans (Dutch if requested)

Location: Pretoria & Online

Showcase: February 2026

Vlyt Art Acting invites actors to participate in a first-of-its-kind scene study of De Nieuwe Ridderorde ‚Äî an 1800s Cape satire by Charles Boniface.

Disclaimer: This is not a paid gig. It is a proof-of-concept project designed to create recorded and live-streamed scene study content. Actors will gain professional footage, exposure, and experience with rare material.

What makes this special:

‚úîÔ∏è Humorous, political satire from early Cape literature

‚úîÔ∏è Multi-character ensemble scenes

‚úîÔ∏è Physical comedy, heightened language, and character archetypes

‚úîÔ∏è Material never translated/performed in contemporary South Africa

**ROLES AVAILABLE**

(All genders considered, age flexible)

**TEMPERANCE KNIGHTS** ‚Äì The ‚Äúsober‚Äù order who are secretly drunk

 ‚Ä¢ Domine Humbug Philippumpkin (Reverend Humbug, pompous commander)

 ‚Ä¢ Stoeleman Puff (Chairman Puff, blustering vice-president)

 ‚Ä¢ Sir John Brute (Banner-bearer, strict but drunk)

 ‚Ä¢ Delirium Tremens (Head medic, comically afflicted by alcohol-related madness)

**NEWLY-INDUCTED KNIGHTS** ‚Äì Comedic, physical roles

 ‚Ä¢ Manus Kalkfachter (Bethelsdorp representative, ‚Äúsheep follower‚Äù)

 ‚Ä¢ Griet Drilbouten (Disruptive wife, hiding/spying, comic physicality)

 ‚Ä¢ Klaas Galgevogel (‚ÄúGallows Bird,‚Äù comedic nickname)

 ‚Ä¢ Piet Dronkelap (‚ÄúDrunken Flap,‚Äù comic drunken knight)

**ANTI-TEMPERANCE GROUP ‚Äî THE COGNAC DRINKERS** ‚Äì sharp-witted satirical commentators

 ‚Ä¢ Quizz (Cunning lawyer)

 ‚Ä¢ O‚ÄôCandid (Gruff old soldier)

 ‚Ä¢ Dr Macthirsty (Phrenologist, parody scientist)

 ‚Ä¢ Call-His-Son (Jolly brandy distiller)

**PROJECT DETAILS**

‚Ä¢ Commitment: 4 rehearsals + final recorded/live session

‚Ä¢ Tone: Satire, physical comedy, ensemble chaos

‚Ä¢ Actor Benefits: First-ever classical South African text on reel, professional recording footage, live-stream exposure

**INTERESTED? APPLY HERE:**

üëâ https://forms.gle/VBvoxiskNvudAngx8

reelsforanyone@gmail.com

I'll look forward to hearing from you.

Thanks!

Hello! Would you like to be an extra on a student film project? This is your opportunity!

I'm looking for actors for my SFU 4th year Capstone film "Coiled Like the Wolf."

This will be a two-day shoot from **November 21 - November 22. Come either or both days!**

Monetary compensation will not be provided, but you will get free food!

Feel free to bring your friends! The more the merrier!

Email me at **mimnom@icloud.com **if you're interested!

CASTING CALL - INDEPENDENT FEATURE FILM (UNPAID)

Production Type: Independent Feature Film
Location: Fairplay, Colorado 
Compensation: Unpaid
Union Status: Non-Union
Filming Window: December 8th to December 11th. 

We are currently casting two male roles for an upcoming feature film. No plot or story details will be released publicly at this stage.

---

ROLE 1 - OLIVER

Gender: Male
Age Range: Late 20s - Early 30s
Height: 5'8" - 6'0"
Role Type: Speaking Role

Basic Description:

A kind, charming, deeply devoted man. Soft-spoken, loyal, and emotionally open. Requires strong emotional delivery and gentle romantic energy.

---

ROLE 2 - ROWAN

Gender: Male
Age Range: 20s
Height: 6'0" - 6'5"
Hair: Brown hair required
Role Type: Speaking Role

Basic Description:
A confident, flirty, golden-retriever-energy type. Playful, bold, and naturally dominant in presence and personality. Requires strong charisma, smooth delivery, and comfortable flirtation.

---

TO SUBMIT:

Email hallowphoriaproductions@outlook.com
 with:
‚Ä¢ Headshot
‚Ä¢ Full body photo
‚Ä¢ Height + age
‚Ä¢ Resume (if you have one)
‚Ä¢ Reel OR a short introduction video

Subject line:
‚ÄúCASTING - [Role Name]‚Äù

---

NOTES:

‚Ä¢ All info about the film will be shared privately after audition selection.
‚Ä¢ Must be local or able to commute to filming location.
‚Ä¢ Non-union actors preferred

Happy Auditioning!‚ú®Ô∏è
